{"tid":856153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華你同我入黎！","createTime":"2018-10-10T12:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T12:53:47.000Z","uid":134683,"like":13,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cedbf76547c383881332c25e7e364db40eda592a","tid":856153,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"曾俊華<br />\n我地知道點解你做財政司長堅持唔派錢<br />\n你一早知到大陸要燒哂香港儲備<br />\n雖然你口講話派錢冇幫助<br />\n其實係盡力留番儲備保護香港、保護我地香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好可惜你選唔到<br />\n林鄭亦要搞人工島繼續燒錢<br />\n但無論如何<br />\n你點愛香港、點為我地香港人<br />\n我地會永記於心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你個名亦會永留青史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19870317064a46db04aeee79fb727e8a7367edf","tid":856153,"uid":54733,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"守財奴唔做野點都好過亂洗錢大興土木"},{"pid":"d45c5fae419a6f97894e5cb6511f1371c843e1f3","tid":856153,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8ffc96d5790d4d24499976d312d68ca22488ba","tid":856153,"uid":54733,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"未來基金（英文：Future Fund）由前任財政司司長曾俊華於2015年2月25日透過《2015年至2016年度香港政府財政預算案》宣布將會設立，作為長線投資用途，用以爭取高回報的利益，並且增強香港政府的財政的可持續性。當香港政府財政儲備降至不足半年的公共開支時，就會啟動預警，香港政府需要就此進行債務融資或者資產證券化，最後才考慮動用未來基金，由立法會批准，甚至中斷未來基金為期至少10年的存放期，以解公共支出的燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n2000億幫香港人儲起黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94150a75d9306e13df55696bd2960fdb05ff04cc","tid":856153,"uid":215894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你走啦 我唔想搞大佢"},{"pid":"c70e832ed16a01f8b81120eeb2dbe06e0bf33474","tid":856153,"uid":201091,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"咁都上到神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e7a4113a64b6d3bf94d18b1c4b7b9ca12a6821","tid":856153,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"曾俊華一早睇穿共匪既陰謀<br />\n宜家變左陽謀"},{"pid":"901ecd22cf0cfe1a7c473413cdcc47f1988993af","tid":856153,"uid":58862,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"on9 財爺黎講佢算最無用 <br />\n因為佢真係無做過野<br />\n<br />\n不過依加果個都係垃圾"},{"pid":"3d7692cbcd9b5dede17568c2855ccae2805603ec","tid":856153,"uid":54733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"總計前財政司長曾俊華過去9年共撥出至少4148.4億元成立或注資各個基金，平均每年撥出460.9億元。當中包括在15年度以「適時儲蓄」為由，從土地基金抽取2200億元成立未來基金；以及成立房屋儲備金，並於14和15年度合共向基金注資725億元。<br />\n<br />\n品客幫香港儲左4000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bfe2acf5401c04b8a35a7548ef0053d272cb6c","tid":856153,"uid":5843,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d7692cbcd9b5dede17568c2855ccae2805603ec","tid":856153,"uid":54733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"總計前財政司長曾俊華過去9年共撥出至少4148.4億元成立或注資各個基金，平均每年撥出460.9億元。當中包括在15年度以「適時儲蓄」為由，從土地基金抽取2200億元成立未來基金；以及成立房屋儲備金，並於14和15年度合共向基金注資725億元。<br />\n<br />\n品客幫香港儲左4000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"儲咁多錢咪又係比土共用撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0650befc64b9bb7cacc5d4480acdc7da5d8d751b","tid":856153,"uid":14758,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"佢想儲多啲一次過比大陸食大啖啲咋"},{"pid":"2